Character       Description                                         Example
.               Any character except newline                        ‘py…n’
^               Starts with                                         ‘^Py’
$               Ends with                                           ‘.com$’
*               Zero or more occurrences                            'gm.*l’
+               One or more occurrences                             ‘ya.+o
?               Zero or one occurrences                             ‘pyth?n’
{}              Exactly the specified number of occurrences         ‘py{3}n’
|               Either or                                           ‘^a|A’